Go to the Anaconda Distribution page (https://www.anaconda.com/download).

Follow instructions for installation.

Create environment once installed:
1. conda create --name radiomics_env python=3.8
2. conda activate radiomics_env
3. cd <path_to_project_directory>
4. Install required packages with: conda install numpy<1.23 pandas pydicom simpleitk matplotlib scikit-learn scipy imbalanced-learn pyradiomics -c conda-forge
